			"id": "http://endonend.micro.blog/2018/10/15/ok-a-second.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>Ok, a second watching of Annihilation left a better taste in my mouth. As a movie, it is visually amazing and certainly creepy. As an adaptation of a book I <strong>really</strong> enjoyed, it took that second viewing to appreciate what it has to offer.</p>\n",
